definition: Tianlin county in Baise 百色[Bai3 se4], Guangxi
woods/forest/CL:片[pian4]/circle(s) (i.e. specific group of people)/a collection (of similar things)

sentences.english: Tianlin county was one of the key forest regions of Guangxi province.
sentences.chinese: 田林縣是廣西重點林區縣之一。

sentences.english: Gaolong microdisseminated gold deposit is located in Tianlin County in northwestern Guangxi Province.
sentences.chinese: 桂西北高龍微細浸染型金礦牀位於廣西田林縣高龍鄉。
